Tested on Debian Jessie for Linux package build. Windows(mingw) needs Debian Wheezy.

build-essential python git-core autoconf scons

Debian build:
  debhelper libfltk1.3-dev libhamlib-dev libjpeg62-turbo-dev libxft-dev
  libpng-dev zlib1g-dev libexpat-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile-dev
  libsamplerate-dev { libcurl4-openssl-dev OR libcurl4-gnutls-dev }
  libxmlrpc-core-c3-dev cdbs quilt libssl-dev libpulse-dev devscripts

NB: the OpenSSL licence conflicts with the GPL. Consider using GNU TLS.



Cross-compile for Windows on Debian Wheezy needs:
  mingw32-runtime nsis unzip

